<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Especially" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Especially,</orth> 1) particularly, principally: <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.2.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. III, 2, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 3.2.247" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 2, 247</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.93" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.3.122" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.1.176" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 1, 176</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.10" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 3, 10</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.1.155" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 1, 155</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.71" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 71</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.1.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 1, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 1, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 5.4.6" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.1.45" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 1, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.468" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 468</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.7.99" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 7, 99</bibl> (Qq <emph>especial</emph>). <bibl n="shak. ant 1.2.181" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 2, 181</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 4.2.104" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 2, 104</bibl>.<lb />2) in particular, apart: <cit><quote>you were born under a charitable star. Under Mars, I. I e. think, under Mars,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 1.1.207" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 1, 207</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>would you proceed e. against Caius Marcius?</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 26</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>drink is a great provoker of three things. What three things does drink e. provoke?</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.29" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 29</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>